                     <interp inst="t18130714-96-person953" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's pocket.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. That is my handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18130714-96-verdict561" type="verdictDescription">
